### Hadith 4:444

*Narrated Ibn Shihab:*

Once Umar bin Abdul Aziz delayed the 'Asr prayer a little. 'Urwa said to
him, "Gabriel descended and led the prayer in front of the Prophet " On
that 'Umar said, "O Urwa! Be sure of what you say." "Urwa, "I heard
Bashir bin Abi Masud narrating from Ibn Masud who heard Allah's Apostle
saying, 'Gabriel descended and led me in prayer; and then prayed with
him again, and then prayed with him again, and then prayed with him
again, and then prayed with him again, counting with his fingers five
prayers."

